{
  "text": "Climate data. Monthly rainfall data at a spatial resolution of 0.05\u00b0 by 0.05\u00b0 were obtained from the Australian Bureau of Meteorology (http://www.bom.gov.au/jsp/awap/). Annual rainfall was calculated as the sum of monthly rainfall. Table 3 . Four process-based models (LSMs) from the TRENDY project [CITATION_1] . Four process-based models from the TRENDY project [CITATION_2] .",
